// The Tarot: A Key to the Wisdom of the Ages

== The Tarot: A Key to the Wisdom of the Ages
_by Paul Foster Case (B.O.T.A.)_

#hm-note[
  TTAO uses the Tarot as a pictorial textbook of the Great Work. It is the "Alchemist's Mirror."
]

- *Major Arcana:* 22 stages of the Magnum Opus and 22 paths of consciousness.
- *Minor Arcana:* The four elements (Wands/Fire, Cups/Water, Swords/Air, Pentacles/Earth) in daily operation.
- *Key Correspondences:*
  - *The Fool (0):* Prima Materia.
  - *The Magician (1):* The Practitioner's Will (Mercury).
  - *The Emperor (4):* The Fixed Salt / The Laboratory Vessel.
  - *Death (13):* Putrefaction / Nigredo.
  - *Temperance (14):* Distillation / Conjunction.
  - *The World (21):* The Completed Stone.

#v(1em)